My heart is broken into a million pieces right now. I can literally hear your voice right now telling me don’t get distracted stick to the script.. but it’s hard knowing you ain’t here. You single handedly changed my life. You said take this minimum and we gonna turn it into Millions. You told me i was special and that nobody could do what i do. Showed me the toughest love.. Believed in me when people forgot who i was and told me if i took care of business that it would do the same for me. I can’t imagine the pain your daughters and family are feeling right now.. just know i listened to every word you said and will continue to pass it down and help others the same way you helped me. I love you LB 😔💔

Today @thebettergeneration we are releasing Kobe 8 Protro "Halo"
Men’s Sizes 5-16 ($180)

Available 8/23

RELEASE DETAILS
*In-Store ONLY*

We will be doing 3 separate releases for these Kobe’s so you will have a multitude of options to participate and secure your pair!

Release 1
Basketball Pop-A-Shot
Time: Noon - 6 PM
Place: The Better Generation Store
4112 Washington Ave
This is not FCFS! This release is our general release method. Come ANYTIME between noon and 6 to sign up and play for a chance to secure your pair! You are playing for YOUR SIZE. Highest scores from the Pop-A-Shot will secure their pair of Kobe 8’s.

Release 2
3 Point Shootout 
Time: 3-5 PM
Place: The Better Generation Store
This release is FCFS! There will only ‘50’ spots available for a chance to secure the Kobe 8’s. We will only be allowing a TOTAL of 10 pairs secured through this process. If you arrive early, please wait in the pop-a-shot line to sign up for the shootout. 

Release 3
2v2 Basketball Tournament
Time: 8 PM - Until finished
Place: The Better Generation Store
This release is our final run for the Kobe 8’s. There will only be ONE team that ends up securing their pair of Kobe 8’s for FREE! This will be an official tournament sponsored by The Better Generation to give true ball players a chance at securing! 16 Teams MAX so spaces will be limited! Sign up is at the store day of. This is fully FCFS, we will be confirming people in line starting at 6:30 but you are free to wait prior. When sign ups start at 6:30 both partners MUST be physically present at the time of signing up.

Drinks available the whole day from @skylab.htx and food will be available from @based_burgers

This past Wednesday, the TBG family celebrated Kobe and the release of the Kobe 8 “Halo.” Thank you to everyone who came out and played for a pair. Unfortunately, we do get a limited amount, so not everyone will be a winner of the shoes. Still, everyone is a winner for being a part of a moment that will forever define Kobe’s legacy. Rest in peace, Kobe; we will forever be grateful for the knowledge and dedication that you showcased was possible to multiple generations of youth. You defined a generation of basketball and non-basketball players alike for generations to come, with or without the sneakers.

Houston we do events like this and unique sneaker releases all the time! Make sure to follow to stay in the loop! 🙏

I think in this post we can also offload extra pairs we still have. We can say something like for one last chance to secure your pair of Kobe 8 “Halos” (Size 5 & 5.5) send us a DM. Required is a note physically in the video or photo that says TBG x Kobe and your shoe size clearly shown. Pairs are very limited.

Check me out on the new cover of @SLAMKicks Magazine. Appreciate the love; it’s been a long time coming! @slam #WearYaKicks @thebettergeneration
